*Additional Eucalyptus Infomration*

This doesn't happen with every template that fails to deploy due to a timeout violation on Eucalyptus.  I used another template below, and it recorded the resources that were created successfully.  Not sure, but it looks like it how certain resources are communicated to be successfully created back to the Cloudformation service.

* _cloudformation template_
{code}
# cat cfn-euca9846-template.json
